            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Igitur fidelium nostrorum presentium ac futurorum noverit multitudo. Quoniam
                        per consilium et <rs key="#Intercessory">interventum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Intercessory" ref="#people/4206">Robberti de
                            Labolita</persName> et <persName key="#Intercessory" ref="#people/3080"
                            >Rainaldi Lopini</persName> et <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Other_palatine_officer" ref="#people/3078"
                            >Stantioni</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">vice principis</rs> et <persName
                            key="#Writer #Intercessory #Judge" ref="#people/3012"
                            >Quiriaci</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudicis</rs> et domni <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Prevosts" ref="#people/4245">Sassoni</persName>
                        <rs key="#Prevosts">prepositi</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/3046">Sancti Angelis in
                            Formis</orgName> et <persName key="#Intercessory #Monks"
                            ref="#people/4241">Mainardi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monachi</rs>, quam et ad salutem et remedium animarum <rs
                            key="#Princeps">principum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Princeps #grandparentOf" ref="#people/3001"
                            >Richardi</persName> scilicet <rs key="#grandparentOf">avii</rs> et
                            <persName key="#Princeps #parentOf" ref="#people/3002"
                            >Iordani</persName>
                        <rs key="#parentOf">patris</rs> nostri, et ob statu nostri principatus,
                        concedimus et confirmamus in <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/84">Sancti Benedicti
                            sito in Monte Casino</orgName> in quo domnus religiosissimus <persName
                            key="#Cardinals #Abbots #Personal_rank" ref="#people/2416"
                            >Oderisius</persName> atque <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabilis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Cardinals">cardinalis</rs> et <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs>
                        praeest, <rs key="#Churches">aecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fruits/vegetables #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Furniture #Books #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3065">Sancti Leonis</orgName> quae est sita
                        foras <rs key="#Walls">muros</rs> nostrae <rs key="#Cities">civitatis</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities #Walls" ref="#places/571">Suesse</placeName>,
                        constructa scilicet a quondam <persName><name ref="Mundus Adus">mundi qui
                                vocabatur cognomine Adi</name></persName>, quae a nobis prephatus
                        Robbertus in <rs key="#Feudum">fevo</rs> tenebat. Predictam aecclesiam
                        Sancti Leonis cum <rs key="#Books">libris</rs> et <rs key="#Furniture"
                            >ornamentis</rs> et omnibus instrumentis eius et <rs key="#Furniture"
                            >casis et sediliis</rs>, nec non et <rs key="#Landed_possessions">vacuas
                            presas</rs> et<rs key="#Landed_possessions #Fruits/vegetables">
                            ortis</rs> cum <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">aquis
                            suis</rs>, et terris cunctis quae ei in territorio predictae Suesse
                        pertinet cum omnibus aliis rebus, mobilibus scilicet atque inmobilibus
                        ubicumque exinde inventus fuerit intro vel foras civitatis Suesse, quantum
                        ad eandem aecclesiam Sancti Leonis pertinet aliquo legali modo, nos
                        prephatus <persName key="#Princeps #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis"
                            ref="#people/3010">saecundus Richardus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs> in prenotato monasterio Sancti Benedicti
                        damus concedimus et confirmamus, ad possessionem et potestatem et
                        dominationem predicti domni Oderisii venerabili abbati eiusque successorum
                        et rectoribus predicti monasterii atque custodibus faciendo exinde quicquid
                        eis placuerit. Remota omni contrarietate et molestatione principum
                        successorum nostrorum vel principum ordinatis, comitum vel vice comitum,
                        iudicum, sculdahorum, castaldeorum aliorumque omnium mortalium. Quod si quis
                        huius nostrae concessionis et confirmationis pagine contemptor aut violator
                        in aliquo esse presumpserit, <rs key="#Penalty">quinquaginta libras auri
                            purissimi</rs> persolvat: medietatem predicto monasterio Sancti
                        Benedicti et domno Oderisio venerabili abbati eiusque successoribus et
                        medietatem nostro sacro palatio. Solutaque paena librarum, hec nostra
                        concessio et confirmatio, firma, munita atque inviolabilis maneat in
                        perpetuum. Et ut hoc firmius credatur et diligentius ab omnibus observetur,
                        manu propria subscripsimus et nostri sigilli inpressione iussimus insigniri.
                        (M) Ex iussione prephate serenissime potestatis, scripsi ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Intercessory #Judge" ref="#people/3012"
                            >Quiriacus</persName> iudex. In anno dominice incarnationis millesimo
                        nonogesimo septimo, et octavo decimo anno principatus domni secundi Richardi
                            <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">gloriosissimi</rs> principis.
                        Datum apud <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/4000">Aversanam</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Cities">urbe</rs> mense ianuario per indictionem sextam. </ab>
